segments.text:
But I have made Esau bare, I have uncovered his secret places, 
and he will not be able to hide himself. His offspring is destroyed, with his brothers and his neighbors; 
and he is no more.

They will take their tents and their flocks. they will carry away for themselves their curtains, 
all their vessels, and their camels; 
and they will cry to them, ‘Terror on every side!’
